  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ensure that the environment and the natural resources upon which human lives and livelihoods depend are managed in ways that sustain productivity growth, a healthy population, as well as the intrinsic spiritual and cultural value of the environment.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This award strives to ensure that the environment and the natural resources upon which human lives and livelihoods depend are managed in ways that sustain productivity growth, a healthy population, as well as the intrinsic spiritual and cultural value of the environment. More specifically, this award includes This project aims to advance the abilities of countries, individually and collectively, to more effectively conduct economic evaluations of chemicals policies. The project supports development of applied research to produce estimates of the value of reducing a set of five types of health risks associated with harmful chemicals, inputs critical to benefit-cost analysis in each country..</narrative>
  </description>
